data.description: Why wait to build when you can step into your dream home now. Welcome to your future home, a captivating masterpiece nestled in Lake Nona's sought-after subdivision! This stunning Coltman A model, constructed in June 2023, seamlessly blends modern luxury with comfort. Offering a spacious one-story layout, this FOUR bedroom, THREE bathroom haven spans 2,883 sq. ft. and invites you to experience unparalleled beauty. Upon entry, you'll be embraced by an open layout maximizing every inch of the first-floor space. The great room effortlessly connects to a generous living and dining area with the well-appointed kitchen, creating an inviting ambiance for intimate dinners or lively gatherings. The gourmet kitchen boasts a range of upgrades, including Kitchen Aid appliances, a wall-mounted canopy hood, cushion-close drawers, a 36" cooktop with 5 elements and knob controls, a combination built-in wall oven with even heat true convection lower oven, and an extended island with seating. Quartz counters add a touch of elegance to this culinary space. The extended island w/ seating is the perfect space to prepare and enjoy casual meals. The master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a lavish shower, double sink vanity, and his/her walk-in closets. Two bright bedrooms share a full bathroom, while an additional bedroom with access to a full bath across the hall can easily transform into your home office. The laundry room features a sink and cabinet for convenience. Throughout the interior, the home is adorned with incredible upgrades that include recessed can lighting, brand new luxury vinyl flooring, a water softener hook up in the garage, and in-wall pest system. Moen faucets and beautiful tile designs add a touch of sophistication to all the bathrooms. The covered patio lanai extends the living area, providing a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor spaces. Enjoy breathtaking sunsets and refreshing breezes from this vantage point. In the outdoor living space, you'll find the lanai pre-plumbed for a summer kitchen, enhancing the potential for al fresco dining. Flood lighting in the yard adds to the charm and functionality of this inviting area. Your peace of mind is assured with a comprehensive security system, including a Ring doorbell and front cameras and the backyard is equipped with DMSS cameras for added surveillance.The location is perfect as you are minutes to the community amenities featuring a one-of-a-kind aquatic and fitness center and the Canvas restaurant and coffee shop. Dog parks, community gardens, great schools, and so much more. Minutes to the VA Hospital, Nemours Hospital, University of Central Florida College of Medicine, USTA headquarters, Orlando International Airport, and the beaches. This home comes with a one-year Buyers basic home warranty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home yours and enjoy a  active lifestyle. Come experience the luxury of this turnkey home now. Schedule your appointment today!
